values: Last night was horrible, mark and i got in a fight at about 2:30 that lasted untill 4, over something stupid that turned out to be really bad.  It was over music and ended in me being a bad girlfriend that he never wanted. Now its the nest night and im still mad at him, HE WONT HAVE SEX WITH ME!!! He never wants to when i want to i have to forcwe him.  I love him but he drives me insane. We had a nice bath together this morning though, for all of 5 minutes untill he got out for no reason. GRRRRR!!!! And my heart still hurts. So does my throught but thats sumthing im gettin use to.

I'm loosing control again.. This time its not about drugs, its about me.  I had the most self-awakening summer. I learned that if people dont like u for u, FUCK EM!! lol But then I found Trevor.. For the first time, sum1 loved me as much as I loved them. He knew me, just as kim and terry and ali know me. Wow and now that I dont have that.. well I've kinda lost control.
